channel.title: Help fast please!
channel.description:
Hello,
I have Project 16 V6 Edit 8 and im want to call it SushiScape. How i do that? There are some NPC that i want to delete... How? I choosed Project 16 V6 Edit 8 because it have a great popularity. On the begin you get an mesage or something, can you change it too..? How can i change my stats to 99?
That ware my questions, you dont have to answer them all, but 1 is good enough.
And i cant start Project 16 V6 Edit 8 ? How i fix?

item.title: Help fast please!
item.dc:creator: @mopar_I mopar I
item.description:
@mopar_I wrote:

Answer to Q1: Go to client.java, search for,

Project 16 V6 Edit 8

Then keep searching it and change it to “SushiScape”.

Answer to Q3: Go to client.java again, search what the message says. Then only change what is in the quotations.

Answer to Q4: Go to client.java, search,

return 135

it should say 135 somewhere, and return 135 replace both and your finished.

Answer To Q5: Go to your desktop (or whereever you extracted your source to) and find a file called “runserver” or something close to that. Double click it, and it should say something like,
(or whatever the port is)

Starting, Project 16 V6 Edit 8 on 0.0.0.0:43594
